Dive into my virtual vintage boutique, where every piece is a treasure waiting to be rediscovered. From classic silhouettes to iconic styles, we're on a journey through fashion history. With a passion for woodworking and a love for the game of kings, I craft exquisite chess boards that marry art and strategy. Explore my collection and discover the beauty of precision in each piece. From classic designs to modern interpretations, these boards are more than a playing surface; they're a testament to the art of chess. Join me on this chessboard journey, where every move is a masterpiece waiting to be made.

With the gentle stroke of a blade, I carve life into pieces of wood, transforming them into delightful companions for your soul. My craft is inspired by nature's beauty, and each comfort bird carries the serenity of the woods within. Join me in the art of whittling and discover the therapeutic magic of these handcrafted treasures. Let's bring a touch of nature's comfort to your world, one bird at a time.

üúÉ Thank you for stopping by Earth Folk! | Processing Time: 1 Business Day | We specialize in small batch, natural body care and holistic remedies to enhance your self care rituals. Effective self care rituals do not have to include toxic formations. Therefore, we stay away from hard-to-pronounce synthetic ingredients and fragrances. We sustainably source high quality wildcrafted and organic raw materials whenever possible.

I grew up traipsing around creeks with my pockets full of newts and beetles. My grandparents raised birds and my sister sold hamsters to the local pet store. I think the core of my personality was formed in gardens, tidepools, meadows, and mud puddles. As an adult, I wanted to share my love of the natural world and inspire the next generation to investigate all the life that surrounds us. I became a biology teacher and moved to the Pacific Northwest, where I engage my students in the classroom with homemade games based on the science we are learning. While my games are designed with students in mind, they are also heavily influenced by the variety of strategy board games I grew up playing. They are rooted in real science, but strategic enough to find a home in any game night rotation. My design process includes sourcing, colorizing, manipulating, and altering vintage art in the public domain until I've created a sort of digital collage that is printed on cards. Text and borders may come from a 1700s map, while organism art might be a combination of two lithograph prints from the 1800s. The result is a beautiful game that is equal parts strategic and instructive. I have been humbled by the community's generous reception of my games and look forward to designing expansions and sequels, as well as all new games, in the future. My instagram account provides updates on my progress and also shares my personal nature photography, along with interesting biology and ecology facts related to the photos. Thank you so much for your support and encouragement!

At Enviro Gardening, we believe in environmentally friendly gardening. Therefore we advocate reusable or biodegradable gardening materials with organic non-GMO seeds.

With deep mindset of environmental health, our research team strives to experiment new gardening methods that are clean, healthy, easy to grow, and high yield.

Your feedback is important for us to develop better products. Please try our products, and share your experience with us.

Have fun with gardening!

I'm Ash - but my friends call me Lemon! We're glad you're here to view our assortment of vintage and antique Loot! We're located in the heart of Kingston, Ontario, Canada - a city known for it's historic past. We source weekly for interesting homeware, oddities, attire and more. We visit charity shops, estates, antique stores, yard sales and vintage markets. We often travel to find our unique selection! You never know what will strike our interest and be available in our shop! Make sure to favourite Lemon's Loot to be updated on future promotions, sales and the ever expanding items available to add to your cart. We appreciate you stopping by and viewing our collection.

The Etsy shop "ThePurityTree" specializes in 100% natural products, focusing on items such as magnesium oil, butter, Himalayan salt scrub, and calendula oil. These products are made using ingredients from the Zechstein seabed and are popular for their soothing and therapeutic properties. The shop has gained a reputation for quality, receiving 5-star reviews for its effective and beautifully packaged products. It's recognized as a top shop for gifts, indicating a strong customer satisfaction and loyalty.

About Be Well Group

At Be Well Group, we celebrate the joy of parenthood by offering a wide range of personalized baby items that bring smiles and warmth to your family's life. We understand that every baby is unique, and that's why we're dedicated to creating one-of-a-kind products that reflect the individuality of your little one.

Our Mission

Our mission is simple but meaningful: to provide families with high-quality, personalized baby items that capture the essence of those precious early moments. We believe in cherishing the journey of parenthood and making it even more special with our thoughtfully crafted products.

Why Choose Be Well Group?

Personalization at Its Best: We believe in the power of personalization. From custom baby blankets to adorable onesies, we offer a wide range of options to make every item uniquely yours.

Quality You Can Trust: Your baby deserves the best, and so do you. We source only the finest materials to ensure your baby's comfort and safety while maintaining our commitment to quality craftsmanship.

Memories That Last: Our personalized baby items aren't just products; they're keepsakes that hold the memories of your child's early days. We're here to help you create lasting memories.

Eco-Friendly Practices: We care about the environment and the world our children will inherit. That's why we're dedicated to eco-friendly production methods and sustainable materials whenever possible.

Join Us on This Beautiful Journey

Parenthood is a remarkable adventure filled with love, laughter, and cherished moments. Be Well Group is honored to be a part of your family's journey, offering handcrafted, personalized baby items that enhance these beautiful moments. We invite you to explore our collections and join us in celebrating the magic of new beginnings.

Thank you for choosing Be Well Group as your partner in creating unforgettable memories with your little one.
